This paper deals with image enhancement, specifically for low-light conditions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of a neural network, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the regularization and learning of subspaces, which could fall under the categories of cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper's focus on practical use and user-friendliness suggests that it could also fall under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
